可我们却要让他烂在死囚监狱里
and instead we're gonna let him rot on death row.

607
00:23:46,560 --> 00:23:48,000
瑞秋  我知道你的感受
Rachel, I understand how you feel,

608
00:23:48,000 --> 00:23:49,390
-但有些事情...  -我想我是
- but there are some things that-- - I feel like

609
