瑞秋  我不能再
Rachel, I cannot provide you

613
00:23:58,020 --> 00:23:59,480
提供资源来支持你了
with the resources and the backing anymore.

614
00:23:59,480 --> 00:24:02,000
好  要是如果我自己能找到资源
Okay, so what if I were able to provide my own resources

615
