我在皮-斯-利律所工作  教授
I work at Pearson Specter Litt, Professor.

618
00:24:10,450 --> 00:24:12,200
大家都知道他们会时不时地
They've been known to take a pro bono case

619
00:24:12,200 --> 00:24:13,490
