好
Okay.

621
00:24:18,280 --> 00:24:21,640
好  你赢了  瑞秋  但这是很不合规矩的
Okay, you win, Rachel, but this is highly irregular.

622
00:24:21,850 --> 00:24:22,910
我不在乎
I don't care.

623
00:24:23,150 --> 00:24:24,010
这也不是我们
That's not a good enough reason

624
00:24:24,010 --> 00:24:25,820
放弃伦纳德・贝利的充分理由
to turn our backs on Leonard Bailey.

625
00:24:29,740 --> 00:24:32,090
不要再质疑我高超的财务能力了
Well, don't ever question my financial wizardry again.

626
00:24:32,090 --> 00:24:33,010
说说看
Let's have it.

627
00:24:33,010 --> 00:24:33,980
我想破了脑袋
I was banging my head against the wall,

628
00:24:33,980 --> 00:24:35,880
想要找到一个阻止吊销的办法
trying to figure out a way to stop the suspension,

629
