我们就能让其他人来帮他运营
we can find someone else to execute the trades for him.

634
00:24:43,400 --> 00:24:44,760
-漂亮  -是啊  但唯一的问题是
- Beautiful. - Yeah, but the only issue is,

635
00:24:44,760 --> 00:24:46,070
