资助那个混蛋的交易员
to bankroll the son of a bitch,

637
00:24:47,510 --> 00:24:48,450
鉴于他的名声
given his reputation.

638
00:24:48,450 --> 00:24:49,510
这不是什么问题
Well, that's not gonna be a problem.

639
00:24:49,510 --> 00:24:50,940
