No, Harvey, this is not nothing.

640
00:24:50,940 --> 00:24:52,460
没人愿意和那家伙共事
Nobody wants to work with this guy.

641
00:24:52,460 --> 00:24:54,520
你忘记在我们对面的朋友了
You're forgetting our new friends across the hall.

642
00:24:54,520 --> 00:24:56,160
什  什么  你在逗我吗
What? What, are you kidding me?

643
00:24:56,160 --> 00:24:58,010
