Sutter's the one Cahill's after.

663
00:25:46,550 --> 00:25:47,610
你逗我呢吧
You've got to be kidding me.

664
00:25:47,610 --> 00:25:49,040
绝对没有
I shit you not.

665
00:25:50,580 --> 00:25:51,600
好吧  我懂了
