Which we're hoping we don't.

674
00:26:06,900 --> 00:26:09,320
-杰西卡  我必须要这样做  -哈维  别紧张
- Jessica, I have to do this. - Harvey, relax.

675
00:26:09,320 --> 00:26:11,080
